#install.packages("Guerry")
library("Guerry")
d <- Guerry
names(d)
##  [1] "dept"            "Region"          "Department"     
##  [4] "Crime_pers"      "Crime_prop"      "Literacy"       
##  [7] "Donations"       "Infants"         "Suicides"       
## [10] "MainCity"        "Wealth"          "Commerce"       
## [13] "Clergy"          "Crime_parents"   "Infanticide"    
## [16] "Donation_clergy" "Lottery"         "Desertion"      
## [19] "Instruction"     "Prostitutes"     "Distance"       
## [22] "Area"            "Pop1831"
library(ggplot2)

# représentation 1
distProst <- ggplot(d) + geom_point(aes(x = Distance, y = Prostitutes), size = 3, colour = "red")
distProst

# représentation 2
distProst2 <- ggplot(d) + geom_point(aes(x = Distance, y = Prostitutes, size = Prostitutes), colour = "red")
distProst2

# représentation 3
distProst3 <- ggplot(d) + geom_point(aes(x = Distance, y = Prostitutes, size = Prostitutes, colour = Region))
distProst3
